{"tid":1069734,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"冷胸週末襲港","createTime":"2019-03-20T07:11:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T07:13:17.000Z","uid":56445,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"97a83e17c85f90a9a5578b0ea0bbad39907084c1","tid":1069734,"uid":56445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T07:11:30.000Z","msg":"溫暖的海洋氣流正影響廣東沿岸，本港今（20日）明兩日有霧，部份時間有陽光，惟天氣在後日的周五漸轉不穩定。天文台預計，冷鋒會在後日中午後橫過華南沿岸，本港屆時將「有驟雨及局部地區狂風雷暴」，離岸海域間中吹強風，周六中午前局部地區仍有狂風雷暴，全日「多雲有雨」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190320&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59385523\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190320%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59385523&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9P3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=5ce1af9e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190320%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59385523&h=6ebcc65c\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190320&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59385523</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c09tc6B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc09tc6B.png&h=14de1544&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"370532b53aa4cf126a8ac7fb89809a5db9c463ef","tid":1069734,"uid":37757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T07:12:31.000Z","msg":"冷手打個熱JJ<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04e041c2326961b6a053a875a7ff7adb26a19275","tid":1069734,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T07:13:17.000Z","msg":"透"}]}